org.dellroad.stuff.vaadin22.fieldbuilder

Interface HasInternalValidator<E extends HasValue.ValueChangeEvent<V>,V>

  • Type Parameters:
    E - value change event type
    V - internal binder bean type
    All Superinterfaces:
    HasValue<E,V>, Serializable
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    GeneratedCustomField, NullableCustomField

    public interface HasInternalValidator<E extends HasValue.ValueChangeEvent<V>,V>
extends HasValue<E,V>
    Implemented by fields that provide their own Validator to use whenever they are bound into a Binder.

    FieldBuilder recognizes fields that implement this interface and automatically registers the Validator returned by getInternalValidator() when binding the field.

    This interface would typically be implemented by complex fields composed from sub-fields for which some inter-field validation needs to be performed. See GeneratedCustomField for an example.

    See Also:
    FieldBuilder, GeneratedCustomField
